76561198029236755,Recommended,248610,15586611,"Posted: 27 April, 2015",all,DragonIroh,"Recommended but needs work.Door Kickers is a fun, simple game of strategy and planning. You get the layout of the house you're assaulting, plan each troopers' route, including throwing flashbangs, securing evidence and breaching doors, then hit Action, and watch as your plan unfolds. It is extremely satisfying to watch your plan be executed perfectly.There are a few things that need to be worked out, however. Planning a trooper's movement requires the use of waypoints, where you order the trooper to look a certain direction, open a door, or use one of their gadgets. Once you've placed a waypoint and moved on to the next one, you are limited in your editing abilities. You can either delete the waypoint or change the action, but youcannot movethe waypoint. Also, if you delete one waypoint, it will delete all proceeding waypoints as well. So if you make a mistake early on, your whole route has to be redone. This makes editing the route very difficult and time consuming.Currently, you cannot export a replay on Mac."
